----
Real time Copy Path
AfterFx Expression
----
Author: GaragePixel
Date: 2023-10-27
----
Plot: Copy the content (points) of a path to another path in realtime
----
Usage: Put this script in the path parameter of any shape of a shape layer.
1. Use ALT+click over the watch to link the parameter to the script and copy/paste this code
2. Change the values if necessary
----
var srcLayer = thisComp.layer("my layer");
srcLayer.content("Shape 1").content("Path 1").path;
